# Minimal scope pinning ONLY — kept narrow on purpose.
#
# /review-impl 2026-05-24 HIGH #1: the previous version of this file set
# pnpm-specific keys (node-linker, strict-peer-dependencies, auto-install-peers)
# that cascade into every npm-using subdir (frontend/, services/api-gateway-bff/,
# etc.) and produce noisy "Unknown project config" warnings on every npm install.
# Those settings were also all pnpm-9 defaults already, so they bought us nothing.
#
# Rule going forward: this file may contain ONLY config keys that BOTH npm AND
# pnpm understand (or warn-free ignore). The @scope:registry form below is
# such a key — both tools recognize it.
#
# pnpm-specific overrides, if needed, go in root package.json under a "pnpm"
# block (pnpm-only, npm ignores) or per-package .npmrc inside frontend-game/
# once Session C creates it.

@loreweave:registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
